parameters.name: レクイエム・暗い場面

parameters: \n<Ameria>"But I didn't mess up today♪ Everyone thanked me a lot～♪"
\n<Luerre>"...You haven't forgotten that I bailed you out, have you?"
\n<Ameria>"Of course I haven't forgotten! As proof..."
Ameria wrote in her journal and offered a prayer.
\n<Luerre>"...Well, fine. Make sure you clean up your room."

\n<Luerre>"It's unusual for you to come all the way to a place like
this. What's the sudden occasion?"
The knight took out an envelope from his breast pocket.
\n<Knight>"Take it. It's a writ from the mainland."

Luerre checked the seal on the envelope and quickly read
through the letter inside.

\n<Luerre>"It comes with the job. Don't worry, I haven't caused any
trouble."
\n<Knight>"...We depart at dawn. Get your preparations in order."
\n<Knight>"Watch your mouth. This is an order."
